body:
# Novation-X-Isotonik-Circuit-Editor
A place to host and share your favourite [Novation Circuit Editor] (http://isotonikstudios.com/novation-x-isotonik/novation-circuit-editor/) Synth Patches... 

When sharing files please include a short description of the patches included within!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
